sources.description:
FISTS FLYIN' -  GUN-SLINGIN' 
The ranch of Red Ryder and his aunt, The Duchess, is being used as the training site for "Gentleman Jim" Corbett (George Turner) for his upcoming fight in Carson City, Nevada for the heavyweight championship against Bob Fitzsimmons.

Director: R.G. Springsteen
Writers: Earle Snell, Fred Harman 
Stars: Allan Lane, Robert Blake, Martha Wentworth 
Genres: Western
